import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import { toast } from "react-toastify"; const OrderForm = () => { const [users, setUsers] = useState([]); const [customers, setCustomers] = useState([]); const order = { order_notes: "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quibusdam dolores ad quam minus vitae cum dolorem reprehenderit impedit nostrum praesentium?", }; const devBaseUrl = "http://localhost:5000"; const prodBaseUrl = "https://www.khamcotailor.com"; const currentBaseUrl = window.location.hostname === "localhost" ? devBaseUrl : prodBaseUrl; const apiURL = `${currentBaseUrl}/api/customer-array`; useEffect(() => { const getCustomerArray = async () => { await axios .get(apiURL) .then((response) => { setCustomers(response.data.customers); }) .catch((error) => { toast.error(error.message); }); }; getCustomerArray(); }, [apiURL]); return ( <>
); }; export default OrderForm;
